library("animation")
## Warning: package 'animation' was built under R version 3.5.3
conditionalNumber <- function(x,x_exacto,f){
  abs((f(x)-f(x_exacto))/f(x_exacto))/abs((x-x_exacto)/x_exacto)
}
funcion1 <- function(x) x^2-2*x+1
newton.method(funcion1)

funcion1(1.1)
## [1] 0.01
funcion1(1.2)
## [1] 0.04
conditionalNumber(1.2,1.1,funcion1)
## [1] 33
# mal condicionada
funcion2 <- function(x) x^3-3*x^2+3*x-1
newton.method(funcion2)

funcion2(1.05)
## [1] 0.000125
funcion2(1.06)
## [1] 0.000216
conditionalNumber(2,2.2,funcion2)
## [1] 4.634259
funcion3 <- function(x) x^2-5*x+6
newton.method(funcion3)

funcion3(3.01)
## [1] 0.0101
funcion3(3.1)
## [1] 0.11
conditionalNumber(13.1,13.01,funcion3)
## [1] 2.491978
